OL,3,C'I've been spat at and abused', says
OL,4,Ccouncil leader stepping down
OL,6,FA Lancashire council leader is
OL,7,Fstepping down from the role, saying
OL,8,Fshe has been spat at and called a
OL,9,Ftraitor as politics becomes
OL,10,Fincreasingly hostile.
OL,12,FLabour councillor Yvonne Gagen is
OL,13,Fgiving up the West Lancashire Council
OL,14,Fleader's post, which she has held
OL,15,Fsince 2022.
OL,17,FBut she will remain a councillor until
OL,18,F2027, when her elected term ends.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
