OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778691955
OL,3,C'I've been spat at and abused', says
OL,4,Ccouncil leader stepping down
OL,6,FShe was the first woman to lead the
OL,7,Fcouncil but says women are now being
OL,8,Fturned-off politics because of the
OL,9,Fcurrent 'nasty' public atmosphere.
OL,11,FThe Skelmersdale councillor wasn't up
OL,12,Ffor election herself last week, but
OL,13,Fher decision comes at a difficult time
OL,14,Ffor Labour following brutal local
OL,15,Felection results.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
