PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778691955
OL,3,C'I've been spat at and abused', says
OL,4,Ccouncil leader stepping down
OL,6,FNonetheless, she has defended her
OL,7,FLabour group's record, especially in
OL,8,Fbuilding new homes. And she said years
OL,9,Fof austerity are to blame for the
OL,10,Fcouncil being unable to afford to
OL,11,Fbuild new swimming pools.
OL,13,FCoun Gagen told the Local Democracy
OL,14,FReporting Service: "I'm stepping down
OL,15,Fas leader and a new one will be
OL,16,Fdecided at the full council later this
OL,17,Fmonth. Politics has changed and become
OL,18,Fquite nasty. I've been spat at in a
OL,19,Fshop and called a traitor.
OL,26,@vD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
