PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778691955
OL,3,C'I've been spat at and abused', says
OL,4,Ccouncil leader stepping down
OL,6,F"I've been a councillor for 16 years.
OL,7,FI don't want to leave local politics
OL,8,Fbut I don't like the environment any
OL,9,Fmore.
OL,11,F"I've also attended Liverpool Regional
OL,12,FAuthority meetings and I think quite a
OL,13,Ffew women are thinking about standing
OL,14,Fdown from politics for similar
OL,15,Freasons. I don't think I'll continue
OL,16,Fas a councillor after next year, when
OL,17,Fmy term is up, because of how
OL,18,Fdifficult it is.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
