OL,3,C'I've been spat at and abused', says
OL,4,Ccouncil leader stepping down
OL,6,FIn last week's West Lancashire Council
OL,7,Felections, Labour suffered losses to
OL,8,FReform and the Our West Lancashire
OL,9,F(OWL) group. The borough now has 13
OL,10,FLabour councillors, 12 Conservatives,
OL,11,F11 OWL, seven Reform and two
OL,12,Findependents. And a new administration
OL,13,Fneeds to be formed by one party or
OL,14,Fmore.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
