OL,3,C'I've been spat at and abused', says
OL,4,Ccouncil leader stepping down
OL,6,FIn addition to Coun Gagen stepping
OL,7,Fdown as leader, her former deputy,
OL,8,FGareth Dowling, lost his Ormskirk seat
OL,9,Flast week. He blamed national
OL,10,Fpolitical trends, saying his own
OL,11,Fcampaign highlighted local work. So
OL,12,FWest Lancashire's Labour group needs a
OL,13,Fnew leader and deputy.
OL,15,FAnd the wider council needs a new
OL,16,Fpolitical administration following the
OL,17,Felections. Labour has ruled in recent
OL,18,Fyears but other parties might now gain
OL,19,Fpower.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
