SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778691955
OL,3,C'I've been spat at and abused', says
OL,4,Ccouncil leader stepping down
OL,6,FYvonne Gagen has a background in
OL,7,Ffootball and leisure. She is a former
OL,8,FWales international footballer who
OL,9,Fplayed for Everton and Wigan, and she
OL,10,Fset up the first women's junior
OL,11,Ffootball league.
OL,13,FShe began working in council leisure
OL,14,Fservices. But in recent years, council
OL,15,Fplans, initially backed by Labour, to
OL,16,Fclose Nye Bevan Pool in Skelmersdale
OL,17,Fand Park Pool in Ormskirk sparked
OL,18,Fpublic protests. And that was seen as
OL,19,Fa factor in Labour's losses last week,
OL,20,Feven though the pools were kept open.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
