PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778691955
OL,3,C'I've been spat at and abused', says
OL,4,Ccouncil leader stepping down
OL,6,FCoun Gagen said: "I know how important
OL,7,Fthe pools are. A few years ago, we had
OL,8,Fa council vision to build two new
OL,9,Fleisure centres but we failed because
OL,10,Fof austerity. We will hopefully get
OL,11,Fsomething in the future. But I won't
OL,12,Fbe there as a councillor, which is sad
OL,13,Ffrom my point of view."
OL,26,@nD@ROUuD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
