OL,3,C'I've been spat at and abused', says
OL,4,Ccouncil leader stepping down
OL,6,FIn addition, she said Skelmersdale
OL,7,Ffaces particular challenges as a new
OL,8,Ftown. It was never fully developed in
OL,9,Fsize as was first planned, which
OL,10,Fimpacts today, she said. Its
OL,11,Fpopulation is around 42,000 but was
OL,12,Foriginally planned to be 82,000. And
OL,13,Fits smaller size hampers investment by
OL,14,Fretailers and by governments in
OL,15,Ftransport facilities, she said. The
OL,16,Ftown has no railway station.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
