OL,3,C'I've been spat at and abused', says
OL,4,Ccouncil leader stepping down
OL,6,FLooking ahead, she said the West
OL,7,FLancashire's mayor role might be
OL,8,Foffered to her, before the borough is
OL,9,Fmerged with other Lancashire councils
OL,10,Fin 2028. She said: "Some people want
OL,11,Fme to stand as mayor. I think I would
OL,12,Fget support from opposition parties `
OL,13,Fbut we shall wait and see."
